const arr = [ 1, 2, 3 ];
function foo() { return "bar"; }
<div className="test" />
```

‚úÖ **Correct:**
```tsx
const obj = {a: 1, b: 2}
const arr = [1, 2, 3]
function foo() {
    return 'bar'
}
<div class="test" />
```

### CSS

‚ùå **Wrong:**
```css
